ActInternational Bridges and Tunnels Act
PrecisINTERNATIONAL BRIDGES AND TUNNELS REGULATIONS applying to international vehicular bridges and tunnels and putting into place requirements concerning the inspection of them. Reports must be submitted to the GoC every two years on maintenance and operations also including any actions necessary to ensure the structures are kept in good condition.
